text: Mikhail Yesin (born 25 January 1968) is a Soviet ski jumper. He competed at the 1988 Winter Olympics, the 1992 Winter Olympics and the 1994 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of the Soviet Union Category:Olympic ski jumpers of the Unified Team Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Russia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1988 Winter Olympics Category:Ski jumpers at the 1992 Winter Olympics Category:Ski jumpers at the 1994 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
